@MosaicCMS_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@TestTenantId = test-tenant-001

### Health Check - Basic
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check - Detailed (includes Azure Blob Storage status)
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/health/detailed
Accept: application/json

###

### Upload Image
# Note: Update the file path below to a real image file
POST {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media/images
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Upload Document
# Note: Update the file path below to a real document file
POST {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media/documents
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### List Files (Images)
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media/list?containerType=images
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List Files (Documents)
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media/list?containerType=documents
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get SAS URL for Temporary Access
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media/sas-url?containerType=images&fileName=test-image.jpg&expiryMinutes=60
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete File
DELETE {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/media?containerType=images&fileName=test-image.jpg
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}

###

### Create Backup
POST {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/backup
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containers": ["images", "documents", "user-uploads"]
}

###

### List Backups
GET {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/backup
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Restore Backup
# Note: Update the backupId below with an actual backup ID from List Backups
POST {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/backup/restore/backup-20241210-123456-abc123
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}

###

### Delete Backup
# Note: Update the backupId below with an actual backup ID
DELETE {{MosaicCMS_HostAddress}}/api/backup/backup-20241210-123456-abc123
X-Tenant-Id: {{TestTenantId}}

###
